AXIS ASSISTANT is an App conceived as a tool to: find a given angle, detect tilt and also to measure a sector size in degrees.

This tool can be useful in many applications such as:

• The steepness of a slope;
• Can be used for hanging pictures, diplomas or photographs on a wall;
• Useful for photography to detect the horizon;
• It measures the angle of an arc (for example in architecture);
• And much more, your imagination is the limit.

GyrOSC is a lightweight utility that sends your device's motion sensors to any OSC (Open Sound Control) capable application over Wi-Fi. Wirelessly control your OSC capable audio or video app by moving and tilting your iPhone, iPod Touch, or iPad.

Wirelessly send:

• Gyroscope {pitch, roll, yaw}
• Accelerometer {x-axis, y-axis, z-axis}
• Compass {magnetic heading}
• GPS {latitude, longitude, altitude, course, speed, time}
• Quaternion {w, x, y, z}
• Rotation matrix {m1 ... m16}
• Rotation rate {x-axis, y-axis, z-axis}
• Gravity {x-axis, y-axis, z-axis}
• Magnetic field {x-axis, y-axis, z-axis}
• Altitude {m, kPa}


Control any live audio or video application that supports OSC messaging. Some examples include Max/MSP, Pure Data, Processing, Plogue Bidule, Isadora, and more.

Features:

- Customize message tags
- Save and load addresses for quick setup
- Screen lock for performance
- Gyroscope orientation reset button
- Control buttons to send OSC messages

GyrOSC will automatically detect the available sensors in your device.
